ActJudges Act
SubjectHon. William A. Jenkins **RETIREMENT AND ANNUITY ** Superior Court of Justice of Ontario
PrecisRetirement and granting of a lifelong annuity to the Hon. WILLIAM A. JENKINS, a Judge of the Superior Court of Justice in and for the Province of Ontario, effective November 9, 2011.
